thread.title: BRIEF-Bank Of Sharjah FY Profit Falls

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Bank Of Sharjah FY Profit Falls

organizations.name: brief-bank of sharjah fy profit falls

text:
Feb 12 (Reuters) - BANK OF SHARJAH PJSC:
* FY NET PROFIT 265 MILLION DIRHAMS VERSUS 402 MILLION DIRHAMS YEAR AGO
* FY NET INTEREST INCOME 466 MILLION DIRHAMS VERSUS 522 MILLION DIRHAMS YEAR AGO
* AS AT END-DEC 2017, CUSTOMERS’ DEPOSITS STAND AT 21.63 BILLION DIRHAMS, UP 10 PERCENT YEAR-ON-YEAR‍​‍​
* AS AT END-DEC 2017, LOANS AND ADVANCES STAND AT 17.48 BILLION DIRHAMS, UP 2 PERCENT YEAR-ON-YEAR Source:( bit.ly/2o0vIPL ) Further company coverage:
